{ "path" : "/hipache", "domain" : "undozen.mian.bz", "title" : "/hipache", "content" : "# run `hipache` in docker\n\nhipache 内存占用是硬伤，已弃用换成 nginx\n\ninstall [docker](docker) first, then\n\n```bash\n$ docker run --name redis4hipache -d redis\n$ docker run -d -p 80:80 --link redis4hipache:redis tutum/hipache\n$ docker run -it --link redis4hipache:redis --rm redis sh -c \\\n  'exec redis-cli -h \"$REDIS_PORT_6379_TCP_ADDR\" -p \"$REDIS_PORT_6379_TCP_PORT\"'\n> rpush frontend:www.wuyongzhiyong.com www\n> rpush frontend:www.wuyongzhiyong.com http://172.17.42.1:8080\n```\n\nreference:  \nhttps://registry.hub.docker.com/u/tutum/hipache/  \nhttps://registry.hub.docker.com/_/redis/", "html" : "<h1 id=\"run-hipache-in-docker\">run <code>hipache</code> in docker</h1>\n<p>hipache 内存占用是硬伤，已弃用换成 nginx</p>\n<p>install <a href=\"docker\">docker</a> first, then</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\">$ docker run --name redis4hipache -d redis\n$ docker run -d -p 80:80 --link redis4hipache:redis tutum/hipache\n$ docker run -it --link redis4hipache:redis --rm redis sh -c \\\n  &#39;exec redis-cli -h &quot;$REDIS_PORT_6379_TCP_ADDR&quot; -p &quot;$REDIS_PORT_6379_TCP_PORT&quot;&#39;\n&gt; rpush frontend:www.wuyongzhiyong.com www\n&gt; rpush frontend:www.wuyongzhiyong.com http://172.17.42.1:8080\n</code></pre>\n<p>reference:<br><a href=\"https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/tutum/hipache/\">https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/tutum/hipache/</a><br><a href=\"https://registry.hub.docker.com/_/redis/\">https://registry.hub.docker.com/_/redis/</a></p>\n", "created_at" : 1422680258249, "modified_at" : 1423052716621 }
{ "path" : "/nginx/ssl", "domain" : "undozen.mian.bz", "title" : "/nginx/ssl", "content" : "# self-signed ssl for nginx\n\n```bash\n# 都以 root 用户操作\nmkdir /etc/nginx/ssl\ncd /etc/nginx/ssl\nsudo openssl genrsa -des3 -out ssl.key 2048\nsudo openssl req -new -key ssl.key -out ssl.csr\n# 注意 Common Name 填域名如 www.wuyongzhiyong.com 或 *.mian.bz\n# 生成的 ssl.csr 也可提交给 SSL 机构做可信的签名\ncp ssl.key ssl.key.orig && openssl rsa -in ssl.key.orig -out ssl.key # 去掉密码\nopenssl x509 -req -days 365 -in ssl.csr -signkey ssl.key -out ssl.crt\n# 上一行就是生成自签名证书\n```\n\n然后设置 nginx\n\n```nginx\nserver {\n    listen 443;\n    ssl on;\n    ssl_certificate /etc/nginx/ssl/ssl.crt;\n    ssl_certificate_key /etc/nginx/ssl/ssl.key;\n}\n```\n\n## reference\n* [/ssl](/ssl)\n* https://www.liberiangeek.net/2014/09/install-self-signed-ssl-certificate-nginx-cenos-7/", "html" : "<h1 id=\"self-signed-ssl-for-nginx\">self-signed ssl for nginx</h1>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-bash\"># 都以 root 用户操作\nmkdir /etc/nginx/ssl\ncd /etc/nginx/ssl\nsudo openssl genrsa -des3 -out ssl.key 2048\nsudo openssl req -new -key ssl.key -out ssl.csr\n# 注意 Common Name 填域名如 www.wuyongzhiyong.com 或 *.mian.bz\n# 生成的 ssl.csr 也可提交给 SSL 机构做可信的签名\ncp ssl.key ssl.key.orig &amp;&amp; openssl rsa -in ssl.key.orig -out ssl.key # 去掉密码\nopenssl x509 -req -days 365 -in ssl.csr -signkey ssl.key -out ssl.crt\n# 上一行就是生成自签名证书\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后设置 nginx</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-nginx\">server {\n    listen 443;\n    ssl on;\n    ssl_certificate /etc/nginx/ssl/ssl.crt;\n    ssl_certificate_key /etc/nginx/ssl/ssl.key;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"reference\">reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/ssl\">/ssl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.liberiangeek.net/2014/09/install-self-signed-ssl-certificate-nginx-cenos-7/\">https://www.liberiangeek.net/2014/09/install-self-signed-ssl-certificate-nginx-cenos-7/</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "created_at" : 1423020859843, "modified_at" : 1423021014019 }
