{ "path" : "/nginx/ws", "domain" : "undozen.mian.bz", "title" : "/nginx/ws", "content" : "主要参考官方文档 http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/websocket.html\n\n```nginx\nhttp {\n    map $http_upgrade $connection_upgrade {\n        default upgrade;\n        ''      close;\n    }\n\n    server {\n        ...\n\n        location /chat/ {\n            proxy_pass http://backend;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection $connection_upgrade;\n        }\n    }\n```\n\n如果有 timeout 问题（默认一分钟？）可以加一句 `proxy_read_timeout 86400;` [refer stackoverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12102110/nginx-to-reverse-proxy-websockets-and-enable-ssl-wss)", "html" : "<p>主要参考官方文档 <a href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/websocket.html\">http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/websocket.html</a></p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-nginx\">http {\n    map $http_upgrade $connection_upgrade {\n        default upgrade;\n        &#39;&#39;      close;\n    }\n\n    server {\n        ...\n\n        location /chat/ {\n            proxy_pass http://backend;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection $connection_upgrade;\n        }\n    }\n</code></pre>\n<p>如果有 timeout 问题（默认一分钟？）可以加一句 <code>proxy_read_timeout 86400;</code> <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12102110/nginx-to-reverse-proxy-websockets-and-enable-ssl-wss\">refer stackoverflow</a></p>\n", "created_at" : 1423021271819, "modified_at" : 1423021568526 }
